      "writtenOn": "2019-10-29T01:22:29Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "this will blow up the length of the cursor. why is this needed? if the intention is only to check that other parameters were same, let\u0027s store only a hash",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 23,
        "startChar": 0,
