        "id": 1114299
      },
      "writtenOn": "2019-10-29T03:07:08Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "clone the request, strip page token and size, marshal, compute hash, compare to the hash in the cursor?\n\nit does mean that we\u0027d spend CPU on this... some implementations require other fields to be the same, but do not actually check it. I wouldn\u0027t be terribly opposed to this, because this happens rather rarely.",
      "parentUuid": "6b2b01b8_641e3bab",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 23,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 26,
        "endChar": 0
      },
